<indentation-standards>

<title>JavaScript/TypeScript Indentation</title>

<rules>
- Always use 2 spaces for indentation
- Never use tabs
- Configure editors to insert spaces when tab key is pressed
- Each nested level increases indentation by exactly 2 spaces
- Maintain consistent indentation throughout the entire file
</rules>

